abstract: Gjok Deda is arrested on manslaughter charges after fight over parking spot in Bronx where victim Ronald Antonucci later died.
lead_paragraph: The police say the man, Gjok Deda, 50, punched a neighbor whose car came too close to Mr. Deda’s children, knocking him to the ground and killing him.

headline.main: A Bronx Man Is Charged With Manslaughter Over a Parking Dispute
headline.print_headline: Bronx Man in Parking Dispute Is Charged With Manslaughter
